# Custom denylist: files that must NEVER be copied to any linked worktree.
# This file is a project-local extension to .worktreeinclude semantics —
# not part of the Anthropic official spec. Entries here override .worktreeinclude
# regardless of any negation (!pattern) in that file.
# Syntax: same gitignore semantics as .worktreeinclude.
.env.production
.env.staging
*.pem
*.p12
*deploy*key*
*credential*.json
*service-account*.json
